title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 175-1.9 - Examination of record after transfer hearing
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 175-1.9 - Examination of record after transfer hearing

State Regulations

The record of the transfer hearing shall be confidential, but it may be examined by either party, including the youth, his parents or his
attorney. Notes
